          "effect": "You expend a number of charges from the kora to cast a spell from its list. \n* **Cantrip**  *read aura*\n* **1st**  *object reading*\n* **2nd**  *augury*\n* **3rd**  *mind reading*\n* **4th**  *read omens*\n* **5th**  *vision of death*\n* **6th** *object reading*",
